sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note right of browser: User types a note

    Note right of browser: User clicks "Save"\nJavaScript prevents default form submit

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa\n(JSON data)
    activate server

    Note right of server: Server saves the new note

    server-->>browser: 201 Created (JSON response)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: JavaScript updates the notes list\nin the DOM without reloading page
